msgid "Shares compare where reports land against where exposure is. They cannot, on their own, separate 'more dangerous' from 'more reported': reporter pools skew by route choice, demographics, app access, and language. Treat over-represented segments as candidates for attention and scrutiny, not as confirmed rankings."
